## 2026-03-28 - No breadcrumb trail for deep token trees
- Added a sticky breadcrumb bar (e.g. `colors › brand › primary`) that appears at the top of the token list scroll container when the user scrolls past a group header into nested content (depth > 0). Each segment is clickable and jumps to that ancestor group.
